1. wanted to show the lines by user request, originally, it was p.line1, p.line2, p.line3, p.line4, and alpha=0 for four
lines, but plot not show.
Solutions: for i col_active0 (= request.form.getlist('check')): p.line(...)

2. when deploy to heroku, couldn't install packages from requirements.txt
solutions: git init
            git add .
            git commit -m 'initial commit' ##updating the modified files
            heroku login
            heroku create
            git push heroku master

3. plot not show on browser after pushed on heroku
solutions: using https instead of http in templates html files.

